{
  "stem": "1415.4",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And she would count us, and walk through the group, look at us, and then at the will of our block eldester, we would either stand there or be dismissed.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Sometimes you would stand there for extended length of time for no apparent reason that I knew of.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And later on, we would get, and we would go and get something.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I don't remember if the bread came at the end of the day, beginning of the day, or in the middle of the day, whatever.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We would get something in our stomachs then.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And then we would go back into our block, and we would do nothing.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "We would do nothing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "There was nothing for us to do in Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "We were just waiting around.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "There was absolutely nothing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So when she asked me-- when-- when she asked me to come and see the head of the camp, we had since gone to another shower.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] shower.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Oh, I forgot to say.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I'm sorry.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I forgot to say, I should really reiterate what our day was like.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we would go-- we would go through the appel, and then the day was nothing.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then we would have an appel in the evening again, I guess at sundown, or whatever it was, I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We would have another appel, and the same thing would-- we would go through, exactly the same.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We would be counted.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "During those appels, quite a few people lost their lives, and it was due to our block eldester.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Like one time, she did something, I don't remember what it was.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She made-- made her kneel down, and hold a chair in her hand, and naturally, how long can you hold a chair?",
      "word_count": 22
    }
  ],
